channel.title: Account Progress!
channel.description:
[center][size=12pt][font=comic sans ms]So I'm working on my pure (skills-wise), and I'm going to be posting updates frequently to let you guys see how I'm doing! Hope to get some support and feedback! <3
PS: You guys can recommend what I should do, etc! Let me remind you that I'm not very rich, so I'm on a very low budget, so don't recommend raising prayer to 99, etc!
[b]2/20/12:[/b] The Beginning
Basically, this is what I started with. Dungeoneering is 1, all other blocked out stats are very low. From hereon out, I will show all stats and even username!
[u]Level changes:[/u] None
[img]http://i.imgur.com/qxAYR.png[/img]
[b]2/10/12 - 2/22/12:[/b] Working on Dungeoneering!
I decided to spend around 10 hours dungeoneering, and I went from level 1 to level 64! Gravite 2H! <3 Note that I have [u]never[/u] done dungeoneering before this, so I think I did very well! Also, the other small level changes listed below are from the tasks I had to perform in the dungeons! [b]Shout out to Rodgerwilco for being an awesome dungeoneering buddy![/b]
[u]Level changes:[/u] Dungeoneering: 1 - 64 Mining: 32 - 34 Cooking: 70 - 71 Runecrafting: 7 - 10 Herblore: 16 - 17
[img]http://i.imgur.com/ErkLB.png[/img]
[b]2/23/12:[/b] Herblore!
I basically trained herblore by making pots!
[u]Level changes:[/u] Herblore: 17 - 66 Constitution: 84 - 85
[img]http://i.imgur.com/ea2uC.png[/img]
[/font][/size] [/center]
